description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of homes foreclosed (out of 10k) within the zip code of 90027. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
name: Zillow Home Value Index (ZIP): Homes Foreclosed (Out of 10k) - 90027
